caption.title: Immunofluorescence analysis of Fab 4E2 with different types of HAdV-infected cells.
caption.p: HAdV-B3, B7, B11, B14, B35, B55, C1, C2, C5, E4, F40, and F41 were individually used to examine Fab 4E2 with HAdV-infected cells using immunofluorescence. Cell cultures with obvious CPE were visualized. The cells were observed by a fluorescence microscope (100Ã—).
